    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh Molly, you&#8217;re bad.  So bad.  Almost as bad as&#8230;well&#8230;me.  </></>My Saturday dance class is right across the street from Zabar&#8217;s, and I confess &#8212; I do have a dreadful mezzanine habit.  So I already have madeleine pans.  Two of them, in fact, since the Scented Madeleine recipe for which I purchased them makes quite a lot. </></>So I&#8217;ll simply have to try your gorgeous chocolatey nutty madeleines.  My impulse is to glaze with dark chocolate, however&#8230;what say you?</p>
